{"tid":1581992,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"好掛住以前每星期都有一大班fd一齊溜冰","createTime":"2019-09-20T00:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T03:30:20.000Z","uid":101839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2eb27b957bbe92c435b305869fe6f6ef48d1f4b4","tid":1581992,"uid":101839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T00:22:11.000Z","msg":"冇溜冰都好多年 <br />\n嗰陣學學下呀媽話要專心讀書叫我停一排<br />\n到之後就反口唔肯比錢我學<br />\n而家大個左番pt有少少錢想學番溜冰<br />\n以前一齊溜開嗰班friend都唔見晒<br />\n自己一個上堂 自己一個練習<br />\n有時都真係幾掛住以前成班人一齊玩一齊練野嘅日子<br />\n又唔係叻 冰場隨便搵一個細路都叻過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n練練下會有少少自卑唔敢練<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"427c1e270e547817a52323afb33cf4a9d4fac94c","tid":1581992,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T00:22:55.000Z","msg":"[公海 文宣整合] 9.29全球反極權集會 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581746</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">9.29 Global Anti Totalitarianism 文宣、資訊、行動整合Channel</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/AntiChinazi929\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAntiChinazi929&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=4a088e95\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AntiChinazi929</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>9.29 Global Anti Totalitarianism 公海</strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FNfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP6crr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=7fdcc3f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/NfHvOU5TXSG9DxQIRNkxLQ</a>"},{"pid":"87134eae9a7dc50e350c97872e590d9a373bc224","tid":1581992,"uid":117906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T00:23:55.000Z","msg":"[公海 文宣整合] 9.29全球反極權集會 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581746\" data-auto-link target=\"_b